# ---- DNH Care blog agent — copy to ".env" on the Oracle VM and fill in ----
#
# Telegram creds are read from SYSTEM env vars (already set on the user's machine):
#   DNH_Telegram_Token   (bot token from @BotFather)
#   DNH_Telegram_ID      (your numeric chat id from @userinfobot)
# On the Oracle VM, export those two (or add them here as a fallback).

# Cloudflare Workers AI (content generation — OpenAI-compatible). Already set in
# system env here as DNH_CloudFlare_API / DNH_CloudFlare_AccountID;
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN / CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID also work.
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=...
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=...
# Optional: override the default model (also switchable live via Telegram /setmodel)
DEFAULT_MODEL=@cf/meta/llama-3.3-70b-instruct-fp8-fast

# GitHub: a fine-grained PAT with "Contents: Read and write" on the DNHCare repo
GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_...
GITHUB_REPO=shafeequealipt-dotcom/DNHCare

# Local working clone the bot commits from (absolute path on the VM)
REPO_DIR=/opt/dnhcare/DNHCare

# Daily post time, 24h, in IST (Asia/Kolkata). e.g. 06:00
POST_TIME=06:00

# ---- Google Business Profile auto-post (OPTIONAL — feature stays off until
#      ALL five are set). One-time setup:
#   1. Google Cloud console: enable the Business Profile APIs AND submit the
#      access-request form (default quota is 0 until approved):
#      https://developers.google.com/my-business/content/prereqs
#   2. Create an OAuth client (type "Desktop app") -> client id + secret below.
#   3. On the VM:  python3 -m agent.bot.gbp_auth login     -> GBP_REFRESH_TOKEN
#                  python3 -m agent.bot.gbp_auth discover  -> account + location ids
# Toggle live from Telegram with /gbp on|off; CTA button with /gbp cta call|learn
# (default CALL = "Call now" button; blog URL kept as plain text in the post).
#GBP_CLIENT_ID=xxxxx.apps.googleusercontent.com
#GBP_CLIENT_SECRET=GOCSPX-...
#GBP_REFRESH_TOKEN=1//...
#GBP_ACCOUNT_ID=1234567890
#GBP_LOCATION_ID=9876543210
# Optional: public https image attached to every GBP post (unset = no image).
#GBP_POST_IMAGE_URL=https://dnhcare.co.in/some-branded-banner.jpg
